official_title: A bill to establish the Spessard L. Holland National Seashore in the State of Florida.

summary.text: Establishes the Spessard L. Holland National Seashore in the State of Florida. Authorizes to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary to carry out the purposes of this Act.
